A vast, crumbling neoclassical bank facade floating in an endless void, its marble columns cracking and fragmenting into thousands of golden coins and paper currency that scatter into a dark abyss below. The architecture shows ornate 1920s Art Deco details mixed with futuristic chrome elements. Tiny silhouettes of people in vintage clothing stand at the edge of the crumbling floor, peering down into the darkness. The color palette shifts from warm sepia and gold at the top to cold steel blue and black depths below. Dramatic diagonal lighting cuts through dust particles and floating debris. Style: Cyberpunk meets vintage propaganda poster aesthetic, with bold geometric shapes and high contrast shadows creating an ominous, prophetic atmosphere.
